gText_Prologo::
	.string "End of the 20th century…\p"
	.string "The KANTO region is in the midst\n"
	.string "of a transition and prosperity\l"
	.string "process.\p"
	.string "The GREAT WAR left the region in ruins\n"
	.string "3 years ago, in these circumstances,\l"
	.string "LANCE and the ELITE 4 took over the\l"
	.string "post-war government, initiating a\l"
	.string "new era in terms of development…\p"
	.string "{PAUSE 80}"
	.string "But not everyone was happy with\n"
	.string "the new government, interpreting\l"
	.string "its rise to power as a government\l"
	.string "takeover, taking advantage of the\l"
	.string "fragility of the region after the war.\p"
	.string "{PAUSE 80}"
	.string "This gave rise to independent orga-\n"
	.string "nized crime organizations, such as\l"
	.string "the FUCHSIA bikers, who were\l"
	.string "trying to recover the pre-war KANTO.\p"
	.string	"{PAUSE 100}"
	.string	"Among all these organizations\n"
	.string "the most respected, best structured\l"
	.string "and most influential is TEAM ROCKET,\l"
	.string "with GIOVANNI as the LEADER.\p"
	.string	"{PAUSE 100}"
	.string	"They are in the process of recruiting\n"
	.string	"young trainers to do their\l"
	.string "“dirty work” and earn extra\l"
	.string "money to fund their projects\p"
	.string "In this situation, we decided to enlist.\p"
	.string "$"		

